After talking with Vincent Massol, decided to change interface to that it accepts something like
 
  <executable>java</executable>
  <arguments>
    <argument></argument>
    <argument>-classpath</argument>
    <classpath>
      <autocompute>true</autocompute> 
      <dependencies>
        <dependency>commons-io:commons-io</dependency>
      </dependencies>
    </classpath>
    <argument></argument>
  </arguments>

with support of <dependencies> not in the first phase
